<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236378>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Perithreticus anderseni, sp. nov. A. Head, B. Wing, C. Terminal antennal segments, D. tarsomeres of first leg, E. thorax, F. aedeagus and gonopods (left paramere in dorsal view, right paramere in ventral view), G. epandrium and proctiger, H. right surstylus. Length of scale bars in µm: 40 (A), 20 (B, G – H), 50 (D – F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/236378/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

